  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6, the boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s], </strong>then peel and finely chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p>",
