    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>butternut squash</strong> for an initial 5 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p>",
