        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash has softened, add your <strong>macaroni</strong> and cook both for 10 min further or until the butternut squash is fork-tender and the pasta is cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>macaroni</strong> and <strong>butternut squash</strong> in a colander</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Pick your <strong>basil leaves</strong> from their stalks and finely chop the stalks</p><p>Grate your<strong> cheddar flavour block</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
