    {
      "instruction": "<p>Carefully transfer the <strong>butternut squash</strong> from the colander into a <strong>food processor</strong>, leaving the macaroni in the colander</p><p>Add the <strong>softened</strong> <strong>onion & garlic</strong> to the <strong>food processor</strong> with your<strong> single creamy soy </strong>and blitz until you're left with a smooth sauce – this is your <strong>creamy butternut squash sauce</strong></p>",
