    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained macaroni</strong> to the pot over a medium-low heat and add the<strong> creamy butternut squash sauce </strong>with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> chopped basil stalks </strong>and <strong>grated cheddar flavour block </strong>and cook for 2-3 min until the sauce has thickened slightly</p>",
