      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your<strong> balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
